<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3650204>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. Schizodon species. (a) Schizodon dissimilis, MZUSP 55143, 220.0 mm SL, rio Jaguaribe, Lima Campos, Ceará state; (b) Schizodon fasciatus, LISDEBE 6981, 275.0 mm SL, rio Solimões, lake Janauacá, Amazonas state; (c) Schizodon borellii, LISDEBE 6977, 245.0 mm SL, Ilha Taiamã, rio Paraguay, Mato Grosso state; (d) Schizodon intermedius, LISDEBE 6984, 233.0 mm SL, rio Jacaré Guaçu, Tietê river basin, São Paulo state." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3650204/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3650208>
    dc:description "Fig. 4. Location of the lots containing the studied species: Schizodon dissimilis (red, orange star marks the typelocality), S. fasciatus (dark blue), S. borellii (yellow) and S. intermedius (white); each symbol may represent more than one sample." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3650208/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

